<br>
The other great thing about skyfire is that you have a chance to get lvl 55+ spells while soloing/small group.  I have seen our lvl 56 monk pet drop there along with other 55-58 spells on mobs that could be soloed.<br>
<br>
The giant fort in BW is hit or miss.  If you play 2am-6am you can most likely get the whole fort to yourself..or have close too it. Even during the day, people are coming and going sometimes empty, sometimes crowded <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
